<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Pago Rechazado - Academy Management</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>

  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; }

    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; }

    .card { background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; }

    .error-icon { font-size: 4rem; color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h1 { color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .details { text-align: left; margin: 2rem 0; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; }
    .details p { margin: 0.5rem 0; }

    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; margin: 0.5rem; }
    .btn-primary { background: #3498db; color: white; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #2980b9; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #95a5a6; color: white; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: #7f8c8d; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="error-icon">✗</div>
      <h1>Pago No Completado</h1>
      <p>Lo sentimos, tu pago no pudo ser procesado</p>

      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Tipo:</strong>
          <% if @transaction.enrollment_fee? %>
            Pago de Matrícula
          <% else %>
            Pago de Cuota #<%= @transaction.installment_id %>
          <% end %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Inscripción:</strong> #<%= @transaction.enrollment.id %></p>
        <p><strong>Orden de Compra:</strong> <%= @transaction.buy_order %></p>
        <% if @transaction.error_message.present? %>
          <p><strong>Motivo:</strong> <%= @transaction.error_message %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; margin: 1rem 0;">
        <p style="color: #856404; margin: 0;">
          <strong>Posibles causas:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="text-align: left; margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #856404;">
          <li>Fondos insuficientes</li>
          <li>Tarjeta bloqueada o vencida</li>
          <li>Datos incorrectos</li>
          <li>Límite de transacciones excedido</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; margin: 1rem 0;">
        Por favor, verifica tus datos e intenta nuevamente.
      </p>

      <%= link_to "Reintentar Pago", student_payments_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Volver", student_payments_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 0.875rem;">
      <p>Si el problema persiste, contacta al administrador</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
